com.google.cloud.spi

Interface ServiceRpcFactory<OptionsT extends ServiceOptions>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BigQueryRpcFactory, ComputeRpcFactory, DatastoreRpcFactory, DnsRpcFactory, LoggingRpcFactory, ResourceManagerRpcFactory, SpannerRpcFactory, StorageRpcFactory, TranslateRpcFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BigQueryOptions.DefaultBigQueryRpcFactory, ComputeOptions.DefaultComputeRpcFactory, DatastoreOptions.DefaultDatastoreRpcFactory, DnsOptions.DefaultDnsRpcFactory, LoggingOptions.DefaultLoggingRpcFactory, ResourceManagerOptions.DefaultResourceManagerRpcFactory, StorageOptions.DefaultStorageRpcFactory, TranslateOptions.DefaultTranslateRpcFactory

    public interface ServiceRpcFactory<OptionsT extends ServiceOptions>
    A base interface for all service RPC factories. Implementation must provide a public no-arg constructor. Loading of a factory implementation is done via ServiceLoader.
